{"tid":896501,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"執政8年經濟成長 民進黨4.8％勝國民黨2.8％","createTime":"2018-11-10T05:48:10.000Z","updateTime":"2018-12-02T10:37:49.000Z","uid":144372,"like":25,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":20,"replies":[{"pid":"7501d385db46041cb58d3c0afe6ac87f4afd5db1","tid":896501,"uid":144372,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T05:48:10.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160425000056-260202\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20160425000056-260202&d=lmhI%2F5UZH7%2FTQnJvND34gARJEaK469wi7EMLOMkgk88%3D&h=76e973cd\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20160425000056-260202</a><br />\n<br />\n據統計，陳水扁執政的8年（2000～2007年）台灣經濟成長平均4.8％，馬英九這8年（2008～2015年）降至2.8％，同期間韓國也由5.4％降至3.1％，香港由5.3％降至2.6％，新加坡也由6.4％降至4.4％。<br />\n<br />\n國發會官員表示，這是因為這段期間發生了許多國際性的經濟大危機，例如2008年底至2009年全球金融海嘯，2012年的歐債危機，皆使得全球貿易量大幅走緩，甚至衰退，這對於以外貿為主的台灣等四小龍而言，當然會帶來極大的衝擊。<br />\n<br />\n扁政府8年間雖也有網路泡沫與SARS危機，相較之下，其對經濟的衝擊明顯較輕微。但值得注意的是，扁政府8年，台灣的經濟成長率4.8％仍高於全球平均經濟成長4.5％，馬政府這8年，台灣經濟成長2.8％已低於全球平均3.3％。"},{"pid":"124f8fff0cecb6bd0133a2ff375b6d5e061bc65d","tid":896501,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"跟著有條友話南部又老又窮就呃盡全部台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d35a96d9b98b54656a208ba8dcf57fa276857419","tid":896501,"uid":164730,"like":0,"dislike":12,"score":-12,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:08:12.000Z","msg":"阿扁係勁人，衰喺發展核武"},{"pid":"150580b4b069903657ac0a896c400486aba88613","tid":896501,"uid":6799,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"124f8fff0cecb6bd0133a2ff375b6d5e061bc65d","tid":896501,"uid":56698,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:05:21.000Z","msg":"跟著有條友話南部又老又窮就呃盡全部台仔<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-11-10T06:12:24.000Z","msg":"騙案層出不窮 最緊要有人受<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\"